    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a separate wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>diced chorizo</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until it starts to crisp</p><p>Once crisp, add your <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> and cook for 2 min further – this is your <strong>chorizo crumb</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1095_step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1095_step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1095_step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
