          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Seeded-tortilla-on-a-plate-1678980934416-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the black beans are beginning to break down, remove them from the heat and mash them into a semi-smooth paste, then add a large knob of <strong>butter </strong>– these are your<strong> refried beans</strong></p><p>Tip: If your beans are looking a little dry, add a splash of water</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1095_step-7-x200.jpg",
