            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1095_step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top each <strong>warmed tortilla</strong> with the <strong>refried beans</strong>,<strong> corn salsa</strong> and <strong>chorizo crumb</strong> – these are your<strong> beany tacos</strong></p><p>Drizzle with the <strong>garlic mayo </strong>and garnish with the <strong>remaining lime wedges</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
